INSERT INTO `oc_review` VALUES (91,124,0,'T*******C','Shipping took only three days. This is my second time ordering from this company and I am pleased. I got a 14 inch closure with three 16 inch bundles. I love this hair, it is so natural and easy to maintain. Will be ordering again.',5,1,'2019-02-27 07:23:12','2019-02-27 07:24:23'),(92,124,0,'T*e','This not my first time ordering from them. But my first with curly hair. Received the hair quick (express shipping ) my bundles are true to length. Loveee the hair as always',5,1,'2019-02-27 07:23:49','2019-02-27 07:24:16'),(87,122,0,'selina','This wig is PERFECT!!!!!!!!! Thank you so much to the seller for you quick responses, and shipping!\r\n',5,1,'2019-02-23 08:54:42','2019-02-24 02:13:38'),(88,122,2,'marry brant','this hair is so amazing. First, the shipping was within 3 days. Once I received It and felt how soft It was I couldnt wait customize and wear. You can keep the curls fresh and popping with a little water mist, curling cream and mousse: Btw, the hairline was lovely I didn’t have that much plucking to do. would recommend, would buy again! more feedback coming when months go by ..:',5,1,'2019-02-24 02:11:26','2019-02-24 02:13:29'),(89,122,0,'L***M','Product delivered very quickly. Seller very attentive and met a large focus on customer satisfaction. The wig has arrived with a slight odor and I knew washed with my shampoo hair. It made a week that I wear the wig and it\'s always good quality. According To my case, I recommend this seller.\r\n',5,1,'2019-02-24 12:50:33','2019-02-25 01:53:18'),(90,122,0,'G***o','I loveeee the hair! I would absolutely order again!!! As soon as i payed for it , it was shipped out the same day! I received the hair 3 days later exactly at the time it said it would be delivered!!! The curl patter is gorgeous!!!! - the seller was very nice as well!!!',5,1,'2019-02-24 12:51:11','2019-02-25 01:53:11');
